OL,3,CSleeping skipper to pay #10,000 for
OL,4,Ccausing fishing boat crash
OL,6,FThe skipper of a fishing trawler has
OL,7,Fbeen ordered to pay #10,000 after
OL,8,Ffalling asleep during his watch,
OL,9,Fcausing the vessel to collide with
OL,10,Fanother.
OL,12,FOn 15 January 2022, Maurice Reid, 44,
OL,13,Fof Fraserburgh in Scotland, was in
OL,14,Fcharge of the fishing vessel Margaret
OL,15,FAnne when he started to fall asleep.
OL,17,FMoments later the vessel collided with
OL,18,Fanchored fishing vessel Blackbird in
OL,19,Fthe Shoreham area, off the south coast
OL,20,Fof Sussex, causing minor injuries to
OL,21,Fthe two men onboard.
