OL,6,FThe crew on the Blackbird had been
OL,7,Fshouting and waving at the Margaret
OL,8,FAnne in an attempt to stop the
OL,9,Fcollision, before pulling on the
OL,10,Fanchor to ensure minor impact.
OL,12,FUnaffected by the hit, the Margaret
OL,13,FAnne continued its journey.
OL,15,FIt wasn't until crew members of the
OL,16,FMargaret Anne looked out the window it
OL,17,Fhad dawned on them what had happened
OL,18,Fto the smaller vessel, only then
OL,19,Frealising their skipper was asleep.
