OL,3,CSleeping skipper to pay #10,000 for
OL,4,Ccausing fishing boat crash
OL,6,FAt Lewes Crown Court, Reid pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to failing to do what was
OL,8,Frequired as master to prevent his ship
OL,9,Ffrom causing serious damage to another
OL,10,Fship or serious injury to another
OL,11,Fperson, under Section 58 of the
OL,12,FMerchant Shipping Act 1995.
OL,14,FReid also pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,15,Fmaintain a proper look out, under the
OL,16,FMerchant Shipping (Distress Signals
OL,17,Fand Prevention of Collisions)
OL,18,FRegulations 1996.
OL,20,FReid was sentenced to eight months
OL,21,Fimprisonment, suspended for 12 months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
