OL,6,FHe was also ordered to complete 100
OL,7,Fhours of unpaid work and pay #10,000
OL,8,Fin costs.
OL,10,FFollowing the sentencing MCA
OL,11,Finvestigator Martin Hayward said:
OL,12,F"This was a dangerous situation caused
OL,13,Fby the master of the fishing vessel
OL,14,Ffailing to adhere to the collision
OL,15,Favoidance rules, which could have had
OL,16,Fdisastrous consequences were it not
OL,17,Ffor the quick thinking of those on the
OL,18,Fvessel in danger. The outcome could
OL,19,Fhave been much worse.
