OL,6,F"The UK fishing industry has the
OL,7,Fhighest proportion of deaths and
OL,8,Fserious injury per capita of any
OL,9,Findustry within the UK.
OL,11,F"Many events involving casualties on
OL,12,Ffishing vessels are a result of
OL,13,Fcomplacency, neglect and flagrant
OL,14,Fdisregard for the law.
OL,16,F"This is unacceptable and those
OL,17,Ffishers and owners who put lives at
OL,18,Frisk will be prosecuted.
